Package org.onehippo.forge.exdocpicker.api

The APIs for service implementation and client accesses are defined.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ExternalDocumentCollection<T extends Serializable>
    External document collection representation.
    ExternalDocumentDisplayService<T extends Serializable>
    The implementation of this interface is responsible for reading title, description and icon link from the domain specific external document object.
    ExternalDocumentFieldService<T extends Serializable>
    The implementation of this interface is responsible for getting currently-selected external documents from the context document node and setting new external documents into the context document node.
    ExternalDocumentSearchService<T extends Serializable>
    The implementation of this interface is responsible for searching external documents and returning the searched result in ExternalDocumentCollection.
    ExternalDocumentServiceContext
    The service invocation context which is supposed to be used by the service implementations.
    ExternalDocumentServiceFacade<T extends Serializable>
    Facade interface which combines ExternalDocumentSearchService, ExternalDocumentFieldService and ExternalDocumentDisplayService.
    ExternalDocumentTreeService<T extends Serializable>
    The implementation of this interface is responsible for providing children and parent items to render a tree list view instead of a flat list view from the searched external data items by ExternalDocumentSearchService method implementations.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PluginConstants
    Constants used in the External Document Picker related plugins.
